-- 01_customer_channel.sql
```sql
-- Pick one channel per customer: the most recent attribution
CREATE TEMPORARY TABLE customer_channel AS
SELECT customer_id, channel
FROM (
    SELECT customer_id, channel,
           ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY customer_id ORDER BY attributed_at DESC) AS rn
    FROM customer_channels
) ranked
WHERE rn = 1;
```

-- 02_revenue_by_channel_city.sql
```sql
SELECT
    COALESCE(cc.channel, 'Unattributed')  AS channel,
    COALESCE(s.city, 'Unknown')           AS city,
    SUM(t.amount)                         AS total_revenue,
    COUNT(*)                              AS transaction_count,
    COUNT(DISTINCT t.customer_id)         AS unique_customers
FROM transactions t
LEFT JOIN customer_channel cc ON cc.customer_id = t.customer_id
LEFT JOIN stores s            ON s.store_id = t.store_id
GROUP BY
    COALESCE(cc.channel, 'Unattributed'),
    COALESCE(s.city, 'Unknown')
ORDER BY total_revenue DESC;
